    "sxs_6RmpLr": {
      "type": "sxs",
      "blocks": {
        "sxs_RzBtGG": {
          "type": "sxs",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/playground_club_image.webp",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "title": "Anytime, Anywhere!",
            "copy": "<p>Are you ready to take your fitness career to the next level? Whether you're a personal trainer, group fitness instructor, or just passionate about movement, <strong>JumpSport Online Instructor Training Courses<\/strong> give you the skills, confidence, and certification to lead dynamic, high-energy rebounding workouts.<\/p>",
            "btn_url": "shopify:\/\/pages\/jumpsport-fitness-club-studio-locator",
            "btn_copy": ""
          }
        },
        "sxs_fWDite": {
          "type": "sxs",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/trampoline_trim.webp",
            "heading_level": "h3",
            "heading_level_display": "",
            "title": "Why Get Certified In Bounce Fitness?",
            "copy": "<p>Rebounding is a game-changer in the fitness industry! Low-impact yet high-intensity, trampoline workouts improve cardio endurance, strength, balance, and core stability, all while being easy on the joints. As more gyms, studios, and at-home fitness enthusiasts embrace rebounding, certified instructors are in high demand.<\/p><h5><strong>What You’ll Learn:<\/strong><\/h5><ul><li>The science behind rebounding and its unique health benefits<\/li><li>Proper form, safety techniques, and modifications for all fitness levels<br\/>How to design and cue effective, engaging workouts<\/li><li>Coaching strategies to motivate and inspire clients<\/li><li>Business tips to help you grow your fitness career<\/li><\/ul>",
            "btn_url": "",
            "btn_copy": ""
          }
        },
        "sxs_4TXM3L": {
          "type": "sxs",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/jft-edu-training-course-19a__10797.1555633540.1280.1280.jpg",
            "heading_level": "h2",
            "heading_level_display": "heading--three",
            "title": "100% Online, Self-Paced Learning",
            "copy": "<p>Our expert-designed course fits your busy schedule! Access the training modules anytime, from anywhere, and complete the program at your own pace. With <strong>high-quality instructional videos, interactive lessons, and expert guidance<\/strong>, you’ll gain hands-on knowledge that prepares you to lead <strong>safe, fun, and results-driven<\/strong> rebounding classes.<\/p><h5><strong>Who Should Take This Course?<\/strong><\/h5><ul><li>Certified trainers looking to expand their skillset<\/li><li>Group fitness instructors seeking new, exciting class formats<\/li><li>Studio owners wanting to add a trending workout option<\/li><li>Fitness enthusiasts eager to turn their passion into a profession<\/li><\/ul>",
            "btn_url": "https:\/\/training.jumpsport.com",
            "btn_copy": "View Online Instructor Training Courses"
          }
        }
      },
